ActForeign Missions and International Organizations Act
SubjectInternational Organization for Migration Privileges and Immunities Order
PrecisINTERNATIONAL ORGANIZATION FOR MIGRATION PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER to grant limited privileges and immunities to the organization and its officials. It also grants the International Organization for Migration legal status in Canada as a legal person.
